channel.title: DSPK character models
channel.description: I have a DSPK client, modified a lot.. How can I remove these '508' character models? They suck. With these shitty 'new' characters that look ugly as fuck (and don't fit the gameframe, ground textures, and objects), the fps lower, the memory usage is double, and the cache size is 10x larger.
